Former President of the Republic of South Africa and former Deputy President of @MYANC Comrade Kgalema Motlanthe, will, on Sunday, 6 June 2021, deliver a keynote address at the wreath-laying ceremony for Mama June Mlangeni and Isithwalandwe / Seaparankwe Ntate Andrew Mlangeni. https://t.co/4ESLcy6V8d